Web app built in django to track your favorite stocks via SMS and email. 

Ft-
* New account creation
* Settings for existing user - Ph no, Alert preference
* Alerts - set minimum and maximum limit for the listed stocks

Require-
* Install PostgreSQL
* Change the django settings for your DB and syncdb to create tables
* List the stock codes in DB using one of the files in convinience_files
* Run update-cache.py and send-alert.py as cron to constantly monitor the stocks

